  "title": "Remote Configuration",
  "diagram_type": "class",
  "description": "Remote config client, product subscriptions, and config state management for dynamic instrumentation. Two subsystems: C++ AppSec RC (appsec/src/helper/remote_config/) and Rust PHP tracer RC (components-rs/remote_config.rs).",

